{"tid":730871,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【異動股】超凡網絡急炒「于日辰」 股價今創上市低","createTime":"2018-07-05T18:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T18:03:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98e17d0d66307860b19bc6ad9a55dc41016a0217","tid":730871,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"筆名「小姓奴」、「于日辰」的網絡作家李文晉，被爆婚外情兼拋妻棄子。超凡網絡（8121）昨日更發聲明，將李文晉炒魷！<br />\n<br />\n超凡網絡今股價受壓，創上市新低，跌6.85%報0.068元。<br />\n<br />\n超凡網絡指就近日若干網上討論旗下一位文案部的李姓員工，已於7月3日正式解僱，而公司及旗下子公司將永不再次錄用該名員工。有傳媒向公司查詢時對方承認解僱的是原姓李的于日辰本人，而于日辰的Facebook專頁昨開始不能被搜尋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530760522_f342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530760522_f342.jpg&h=2eb77dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180705/58402126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402126&d=uOklBcEPVMBt4WtBUitnIHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a67faa4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402126&h=c01293bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180705/58402126</a>"}]}